"/rest/api/content/3741450281/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3741450281/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3741450281/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3741450281","tinyui":"/x/KQAC3w","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3741450281","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3741450281/Nuevos+Medios+de+Pago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3741450281"}},{"id":"3711533057","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3711533057","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzcxMTUzMzA1Nw==","status":"current","title":"Nuevos medios de pago -  QR en VPOS - Tasking y Estimación","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":346433015},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3711533057/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3711533057/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3711533057/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3711533057/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3711533057","tinyui":"/x/AYA53Q","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3711533057","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3711533057/Nuevos+medios+de+pago+-+QR+en+VPOS+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3711533057"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"a413292f-920a-45ec-b34c-2d4151ca3461\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento tiene el seguimiento de la iniciativa para agregar QR a los Nuevos Medios de Pago.</p><p><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/browse/PEV20-583?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNGJiYmY4YmVmMWQwNDVjNmJmMjQ2YTA3MDlhOWFhYTMiLCJwIjoiaiJ9\">PEV20-583 - Nuevos Medios de Pago - QR</a></p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /> </p><p>Fecha de Entrega: <time datetime=\"2025-03-21\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"1011\" data-layout=\"center\" ac:local-id=\"83d80421-149f-45eb-a0fa-598d6df873ed\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 322.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 171.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 117.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 119.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 275.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Titular</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Inicio</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Fin</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Comentarios</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-584 - [vpos-portal] Agregar tab al iframe para mostrar el QR. Agregar comportamiento para que cargue la imagen solo al primer click. Subsiguientes clicks no cargan la imagen.</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"e4473a4b-2ba5-4e32-8c9f-74b03b5e79bc\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p><time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /> </p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-585 - [vpos-portal] Implementar endpoint que consuma vpos-service y genere el alias y el qr para un SingleBuy dado</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"d6428de4-9e0e-4e8c-9f1c-f3ecb71659a8\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p><time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-586 - Limitar pesta&ntilde;a de QR a flujos de single_buy y comercios que lo tengan habilitado</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"76798446-645d-499f-9b44-d7e0723ada0e\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p><time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-587 - [vpos-portal] Agregar endpoint para recibir confi rmaciones de pagos QR desde vpos-service para actualizar vista de usuarios</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"30220b3f-be8d-4386-aa7c-cfe5718d6423\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p><time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-588 - [vpos-portal] Configuraci&oacute;n de websockets en el c&oacute;digo javascript de vpos-portal para poder recibir notifi caciones del pago y redirigir al usuario correspondientemente.</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"667fcbc8-a3a4-45a0-a7cd-8ea4c141ad0b\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p><time datetime=\"2025-02-11\" /></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-589 - [vpos-portal] Configuraci&oacute;n de websockets en el c&oacute;digo javascript de vpos-portal para poder recibir notifi caciones del pago y redirigir al usuario correspondientemente.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-590 - [vpos-service] Agregar columnas alias y qr_url en la tabla operations, asociado a un SingleBuy.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-591 - [vpos-service] Crear endpoint para generar QR de un determinado process_id</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-592 - [vpos-service] Eliminar de manera periodica los QRs. Ver de referencia selling-service. Tiempo de vida: 1 mes a partir del created_at</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-593 - [vpos-service] Crear endpoint de confi rmaci&oacute;n para que billing-service-public-proxy confi rme los pagos que se hayan hecho a trav&eacute;s de pago QR con App de entidad bancaria.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-594 - [vpos-service] En la operaci&oacute;n de get_buy debemos agregar en la respuetsa para que vpos-portal pueda distinguir si mostrar o no la tab de QR</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-595 - [commerce-suite] Agregar a la pantalla de personalizaci&oacute;n de aplicaci&oacute;n de vpos la posibilidad de encender/apagar pagos QR.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-596 - [billing-service-public-proxy] Editar las operaciones confirm y confirm_payment_with_confirmation</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-597 - [billing-service-public-proxy] Adaptar la operaci&oacute;n confirmation_by_entity_transaction_id para que funcione con QRs de vpos</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-598 - [billing-service-public-proxy] Adaptar la operaci&oacute;n decode_qr_code para soportar el decode de QRs de vpos</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>PEV20-599 - [nginx] Debuggear y revisar configuraci&oacute;n relacionada a websockets en vpos-portal</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3741483042"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":93},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3741483042/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3741483042/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3741483042/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3741483042/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3741483042","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3741483042/Seguimiento+Nuevos+Medios+de+Pago+-+QR","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3741483042","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3741483042","tinyui":"/x/IoAC3w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}